---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Roast Bacon-Veggie Salad with Japanese Mayo & Crushed Peanuts
description: The magic in this dish is the juicy chicken thigh, perfectly browned and then drizzled with our tasty Japanese mayo. Add a nourishing roasted veggie salad and some crushed peanuts in the mix, and you've got a delicious Asian-inspired meal on the table in no time!
